nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The Partner Central home page presents a collection of headline sections that highlight the latest partner‑focused news, product announcements, and program updates, such as joint messaging with Cisco, Pure Storage, and Nutanix, marketing insights, new product availability, and the upcoming FY26 Elevate Partner Program. Its primary purpose is to give distributors a quick, centralized view of current initiatives and resources that drive the hybrid‑cloud and partner ecosystem. The visible features are a series of banner‑style headers and brief introductory copy inviting users to catch up on recent stories and insights.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Sales Data – Bookings” view within Partner Central that presents a tabular list of booking opportunities, showing details such as opportunity name and ID, customer and account segment, opportunity type and stage, forecast category, associated products, and the reseller and distributor involved. Its primary purpose is to let a logged‑in distributor quickly browse, filter and assess current booking opportunities across the partner ecosystem. Key visible sections include the top navigation bar with the Partner Central logo, a “View As” selector and date filter, and the main data table that organizes the opportunity information into the columns described.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Sales Data” view within Partner Central that lists booking opportunities filtered by the “New Logo” sub‑category. Its primary function is to let a logged‑in distributor examine detailed opportunity records—showing fields such as opportunity name and ID, customer, account segment, type, stage, forecast category, product lineup, and the associated reseller and distributor. The main visible sections are the page header with navigation controls (including a “View As” selector) and a tabular grid that presents each opportunity as a row across the defined columns.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Renewals Data – Bookings” view within Partner Central, showing a table that would list renewal‑related booking opportunities (currently empty). Its primary function is to let a distributor review and manage renewal bookings across their partner portfolio. The layout includes the standard Partner Central header (with © Nutanix, navigation tabs, and a “View As” selector) followed by the main content area where the bookings table would be displayed.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Sales Data – Bookings” view within Partner Central, filtered to the “Others” sub‑category. Its purpose is to let a distributor examine booking information for that segment, presenting the data in a table layout (which currently shows no opportunities) under the main navigation headers such as “Partner Central,” “View As,” and “Sales Data.” The visible sections include the global page header, the sub‑category filter in the URL, and the central table area where booking records would be listed.
